Public Suffix List
------------------
`crates/cerberus-consent/src/psl_snapshot.dat` is a comment-stripped snapshot
of the Public Suffix List (VERSION 2026-06-10_05-34-24_UTC, ICANN and private
sections), obtained from https://publicsuffix.org/list/public_suffix_list.dat.

The Public Suffix List is licensed under the Mozilla Public License, v. 2.0.
A copy of the MPL is available at https://mozilla.org/MPL/2.0/. The snapshot is
data consumed by Cerberus' own matcher (`cerberus-consent/src/psl.rs`); no MPL
code is included. To refresh: re-download the list, strip `//` comment lines
and blank lines, and replace the snapshot file.

